my router config:
new Router({
  mode: 'history',
  routes: [
    {
      path:  '/index',
      components: {
        Left: Left,
        Middle: Middle,
        Right: Right
      }
    },
    {
      path: '/working',
      components: {
        Left: workingLeft,
        Middle: Middle,
